Description:
Just when you have a moment to rest, the ship calls to battle station, as an enemy vessel appears on the horizon.

The sailors prepare the ship for the upcoming battle with a pirate sloop. Before you realise, you are in the middle of a fight. 

There are pirates everywhere, but you have the chance to board the enemy ship and maybe claim it for you.
